                     <interp inst="t18220417-102-person1011" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a carpenter. I saw the prisoner looking into Wood's cart; he got on the tail board and pulled the coat from the front, and put it against the tail board, went a few yards further, and then pulled it quite out, and ran off twisting it round his arm; I pursued, he ran as hard as he could and dropped it. I saw him taken.</p>
